    • saveStoreOrdersToFile

      public void saveStoreOrdersToFile()
      Save the orders with the string format in the file. The system shall be able to export the store orders and save them in a text file, which includes a list of store orders. Each store order shall include the order number, the list of pizzas ordered, and the order total.
